1
00:00:00,213 --> 00:00:03,895
<i>Selamat datang kembali
di "United States Of Horror".</i>

2
00:00:03,960 --> 00:00:08,382
<i>Kau kembali ke dunia
yang dipenuhi rasa sakit.</i>

3
00:00:08,407 --> 00:00:10,706
<i>Surganya kehancuran,</i>

4
00:00:10,730 --> 00:00:13,155
<i>Di mana Malaikat Maut
melihat semuanya...</i>

5
00:00:13,197 --> 00:00:17,299
