41
00:04:39,589 --> 00:04:41,339
Sial! Aku hampir sampai!

42
00:04:48,978 --> 00:04:50,872
Camille?

43
00:05:01,369 --> 00:05:04,740
- Hei, sayang!
- Aku datang!

44
00:05:04,817 --> 00:05:06,865
- Hei. Ada apa?
- Hei.

45
00:05:06,907 --> 00:05:08,511
Aku mendengar
